libsource.description:
OBD-II Connector OBDII is an on board diagnostics standard that is used on a large variety of cars. Here is the connector we sell at SparkFun:
  • OBD-II connector (DEV-09911)
  • Info and Pinout (sorry, no datasheet)
We do not use this connector on any active designs, however, if you're looking for OBDII tech, please check out these:
  • SparkFun OBD related products
22uF ceramic capacitors A capacitor is a passive two-terminal electrical component used to store electrical energy temporarily in an electric field.
0.1uF ceramic capacitors A capacitor is a passive two-terminal electrical component used to store electrical energy temporarily in an electric field.
10.0uF ceramic capacitors A capacitor is a passive two-terminal electrical component used to store electrical energy temporarily in an electric field.
GNSS Module NEO M8, VCC 2.7V to 3.6V

Battery - Single Cell A variety of battery chemistries, sizes, and footprints. Device List:
  • 20MM_PTH - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 20mm (PTH)
  • 6.8MM_PTH - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 6.8MM(SMD)
  • 12MM_SMD - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 12mm (SMD)
  • 12MM_PTH - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 12mm (PTH)
  • 20MM_SMD - 20mm Coin Cell Battery Holder (SMD) (2 legs)
    • Used on the Big Time Watch Kit
  • 20MM_SMD_4LEGS - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 20mm (SMD)
  • 20MM_SMD_4LEGS_OVERPASTE - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 20mm (SMD) (Over-paste on the legs)
  • 24.5MM_PTH - Coin Cell Battery Holder - 24.5mm (PTH)
  • 9V - 9V Battery Holder - PC Mount
    • Used on the SparkFun SparkPunk Sound Kit and SparkFun SparkPunk Sequencer Kit
  • 18650 - Battery Holder - 18650 (PTH)
  • AA - Battery Holder - 1xAA (PTH)
  • AAA - Battery Holder - 1xAAA (PTH)
  • AA_KIT - Battery Holder - 1xAA (PTH)
    • Special kit package - pads only have exposed copper on one side of the board.
  • AAA_KIT - Battery Holder - 1xAAA (PTH)
    • Special kit package - pads only have exposed copper on one side of the board.

Ferrite Bead (blocks, cores, rings, chokes, etc.) Inductor with layers of ferrite used to suppress high frequencies. Often used to isolate high frequency noise. SparkFun Products:
  • IOIO-OTG - V2.2
  • SparkFun SAMD21 Mini Breakout
  • SparkFun 6 Degrees of Freedom Breakout - LSM6DS3
  • SparkFun SAMD21 Dev Breakout

Red SMD LED Used in manufacturing of most products at SparkFun Packages:
  • 0603 - SMD 0603 package [Product Link]
  • 0603 SMART - SMD 0603 SMART package ( more efficient and expensive)[Product Link]
  • 1206 - SMD1206 package [Product Link]
      • SparkFun Products:
      • Pro Mini 328 -5V
      • RedBoard
